# Usage Guide

## Basic Usage
```python
from {{ module_name }} import CONF, hello

# Simple greeting
print(hello())

# Access configuration
print(CONF.workspace.data_dir)
```

## Working with Configuration

### Accessing Settings
```python
from {{ module_name }} import CONF

# Workspace paths
data_path = CONF.workspace.data_dir
output_path = CONF.workspace.output_dir
models_path = CONF.workspace.models_dir

# Create all workspace directories
CONF.workspace.ensure_directories()
```

### Converting to Dictionary
```python
from {{ module_name }} import CONF

# Get all settings as dict
settings_dict = CONF.to_dict()
print(settings_dict)
```

## Utility Functions
